TGIF! 💝 We’re 1 month into CB and embracing all the changes. Wouldn’t it be nice to embrace the weekend with a cold glass of cold drip coffee? What flavour would you choose? 😋
. 
Win a 500ml cold drip coffee!
1. Like this post & follow @cafe4yousg
2. Comment below your favourite cold drip flavour and tag 2 friends
. 
Contest ends on 9th May, 12pm and 10 lucky winners will have a bottle of cold drip delivered to your doorstep! 
#colddrip #coffee #dailydose #caffeine #delivery #cbthings #chill #tgif #giveaway #embrace #flavour #weekend #mayholiday #graduation #stayhomesg #stayunitedsg #supportlocal
Ive so glued to the thai milk tea, hadnt try the coffee series yet. Im 3mins walkable distance away, and i wanna try the TOFFEE RABBIT please! 😎 @eunwong91 @alansyk
@alansyk ya man.. You traveled all the way from woodlands to eat there. Max dedication man
Ever since my friend @sunnyfishballs introduce me to @cafe4yousg I have fall in love with the food and drink, especially Thai milk tea. I would love to try fragaria Kitty! @miao.ling.y @stephy_cjy
I love the black cold coffee, it's so refreshing!! @jeannebeautiful @chooiwaituck

I ❤️ the Charcoal Donkey, it is difficult to get good cold drip black coffee. Charcoal Donkey is so aromatic, bitter in taste yet not acidic at all. I also fall for the Tropical Monkey and Abrabica Puppy.
